{"lemma":"نُهْبَةُ","slug":"نُهْبَةُ","root":"ن.ه.ب","root_slug":"ن-ه-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ن-ه-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n40599"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%86%D9%8F%D9%87%D9%92%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n40599","headword_ar":"نُهْبَةٌ","root":"nhb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuhobaY","text_ar":"نُهْبَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, Mgh, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuhayobaY","text_ar":"نُهَيْبَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuh~ayobaY","text_ar":"نُهَّيْبَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Spoil, plunder,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"booty; a thing taken as spoil:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb:) and also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Spoliation; a taking of spoil, plunder,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"booty:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) substs. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nahaba","text_ar":"نَهَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) and substs. in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AinotihaAbN","text_ar":"اِنْتِهَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Lh, Mgh:) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuhobaY","text_ar":"نُهْبَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is explained in the Towsheeh as signifying the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"taking of a Muslim's property by force:"},{"kind":"text","text":"it is said, [of Mohammad,] in a trad., that he seattered some articles of property, and the people did not take them; so he asked them why they did not take; and they replied"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awalayosa qado nahayota","text_ar":"اَوَلَيْسَ قَدْ نَهَيْتَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eani Aln~uhobaY","text_ar":"عَنِ النُّهْبَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Hast thou not forbidden spoliation?"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; but he said"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~amaA nahayotu Eano nuhobaY AlEasaAkiri","text_ar":"اـِنَّمَا نَهَيْتُ عَنْ نُهْبَى العَسَاكِرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have only forbidden soldiers' spoliation"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nahobN","text_ar":"نَهْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["Lh","Mgh","Msb","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}